{
  "stem": "3150.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "From my father's family, none of them survived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was one of four.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "None of them-- none of them survived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my grandmother one of them that passed away while she was in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the other one was liquidated while the ghetto was liquidated in 1941.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, all of them were living in Austrazetz, yeah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Non-Jews-- the-- the only Jew-- there was one family that I-- I can remember.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was non-Jews-- there were a lot of Ukraines and Czech.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A lot of Czechoslovakian-- and they had big farms in our area at that time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my-- well, we had a store.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "While my-- while my father used to go into countryside, my mother used to be in the store, and also one of her sisters, the one that was survived.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they used-- they used to handle the store.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my grandmother always lived with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Since the day I can remember, she always lived with us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she, like, actually took care of us most of the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She always lived with us, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in 1941, when the-- when the Germans invaded Russia, and it only took them, if I can remember exactly, probably like, 10 days to come in-- I mean, to-- to-- to overrun us.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first big danger-- it was a month or five weeks after they came in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one day, they-- in the street, they picked up every able man that looked like a grown man, if he was 13 or 14 or 15.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They picked him up, and at that time, they probably picked up between 80, and 90 men only.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took them out four kilometers in a-- in a-- in a forest.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
